{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Illegal wildlife trade in Brazil"},{"time":4000,"text":"is one of the major threats against our fauna,"},{"time":7000,"text":"especially birds,"},{"time":9000,"text":"and mainly to supply the pet market"},{"time":12000,"text":"with thousands of animals taken from nature every month,"},{"time":16000,"text":"and transported far from their origins,"},{"time":19000,"text":"to be sold mainly in Rio de Janeiro and São Paulo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":23000,"text":"It is estimated that"},{"time":25000,"text":"all kinds of illegal wildlife trade in Brazil"},{"time":28000,"text":"withdraw from nature"},{"time":30000,"text":"almost 38 million animals every year,"},{"time":34000,"text":"a business worth almost two billion dollars."},{"time":38000,"text":"The police intercepts"},{"time":40000,"text":"these huge cargos with live animals,"},{"time":43000,"text":"intended to supply the pet market,"},{"time":46000,"text":"or they seize the animals directly from the people's houses,"},{"time":50000,"text":"and this is how we end up, every month,"},{"time":53000,"text":"with thousands of seized animals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":57000,"text":"And for us to understand what happens with them,"},{"time":59000,"text":"we're going to follow Brad."},{"time":63000,"text":"In the eyes of many people,"},{"time":65000,"text":"after the animals are seized,"},{"time":67000,"text":"they say, \"Yay, justice has been served."},{"time":70000,"text":"The good guys arrived,"},{"time":72000,"text":"took the cute, mistreated animals"},{"time":74000,"text":"from the hands of the evil traffickers,"},{"time":76000,"text":"and everyone lived happily ever after.\""},{"time":81000,"text":"But did they? Actually, no,"},{"time":83000,"text":"and this is where many of our problems begin."},{"time":86000,"text":"Because we have to figure out"},{"time":88000,"text":"what to do with all these animals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91000,"text":"In Brazil, they are usually first sent"},{"time":93000,"text":"to governmental triage facilities,"},{"time":96000,"text":"in which most of the cases,"},{"time":98000,"text":"the conditions are as bad as"},{"time":100000,"text":"with the traffickers."},{"time":102000,"text":"In 2002, these centers received"},{"time":105000,"text":"45,000 animals,"},{"time":108000,"text":"of which 37,000 were birds."},{"time":111000,"text":"And the police estimates that we seize"},{"time":113000,"text":"only five percent of what's being trafficked."},{"time":117000,"text":"Some lucky ones -- and among them, Brad --"},{"time":120000,"text":"go to serious rehabilitation centers after that."},{"time":123000,"text":"And in these places they are cared for."},{"time":127000,"text":"They train their flying,"},{"time":129000,"text":"they learn how to recognize the food they will find in nature,"},{"time":132000,"text":"and they are able to socialize"},{"time":134000,"text":"with others from the same species."},{"time":136000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":138000,"text":"But then what?"},{"time":140000,"text":"The Brazil Ornithological Society --"},{"time":142000,"text":"so now we're talking only birds --"},{"time":145000,"text":"claims that we have too little knowledge"},{"time":148000,"text":"about the species in nature."},{"time":150000,"text":"Therefore, it would be too risky"},{"time":152000,"text":"to release these animals,"},{"time":154000,"text":"both for the released and for the natural populations."},{"time":158000,"text":"They also claim that we spend too many resources"},{"time":161000,"text":"in their rehabilitation."},{"time":163000,"text":"Following this argument,"},{"time":165000,"text":"they suggest that all the birds"},{"time":167000,"text":"seized from non-threatened species"},{"time":170000,"text":"should be euthanized."},{"time":172000,"text":"However, this would mean having killed"},{"time":176000,"text":"26,267 birds,"},{"time":180000,"text":"only in the state of São Paulo, only in 2006."}]},{"cues":[{"time":185000,"text":"But, some researchers, myself included --"},{"time":189000,"text":"some NGOs and some people from the Brazilian government --"},{"time":193000,"text":"believe there is an alternative."},{"time":195000,"text":"We think that if and when the animals meet"},{"time":199000,"text":"certain criteria concerning their health,"},{"time":202000,"text":"behavior, inferred origin"},{"time":204000,"text":"and whatever we know about the natural populations,"},{"time":208000,"text":"then technically responsible releases are possible,"},{"time":212000,"text":"both for the well-being of the individual,"},{"time":215000,"text":"and for the conservation of the species and their ecosystems,"},{"time":219000,"text":"because we will be returning genes for these populations --"},{"time":223000,"text":"which could be important for them"},{"time":225000,"text":"in facing environmental challenges --"},{"time":228000,"text":"and also we could be returning"},{"time":230000,"text":"potential seed dispersers, predators, preys, etc."}]},{"cues":[{"time":236000,"text":"All of these were released by us."},{"time":238000,"text":"On the top, the turtles are just enjoying freedom."},{"time":240000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":242000,"text":"On the middle,"},{"time":244000,"text":"this guy nested a couple of weeks after the release."},{"time":247000,"text":"And on the bottom, my personal favorite,"},{"time":250000,"text":"the little male over there,"},{"time":252000,"text":"four hours after his release"},{"time":254000,"text":"he was together with a wild female."},{"time":258000,"text":"So, this is not new, people have been"},{"time":260000,"text":"doing this around the world."},{"time":262000,"text":"But it's still a big issue in Brazil."},{"time":264000,"text":"We believe we have performed"},{"time":266000,"text":"responsible releases."},{"time":268000,"text":"We've registered released animals mating in nature"},{"time":272000,"text":"and having chicks."},{"time":274000,"text":"So, these genes are indeed going back to the populations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":279000,"text":"However this is still a minority"},{"time":281000,"text":"for the very lack of knowledge."},{"time":284000,"text":"So, I say, \"Let's study more, let's shed light on this issue,"},{"time":287000,"text":"let's do whatever we can.\""},{"time":289000,"text":"I'm devoting my career to that."},{"time":291000,"text":"And I'm here to urge each and every one of you"},{"time":294000,"text":"to do whatever is in your reach:"},{"time":296000,"text":"Talk to your neighbor, teach your children,"},{"time":299000,"text":"make sure your pet is from a legal breeder."},{"time":302000,"text":"We need to act, and act now,"},{"time":305000,"text":"before these ones are the only ones left."},{"time":308000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":310000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}